[In April 2014 an event of FMD was reported by Zimbabwe. Serotype SAT 2 was identified by the Botswana Vaccine Institute.

According to the last follow-up no. 4, dated 25 Feb 2015, this event is still continuing. 20 outbreaks have been reported and these were located in the provinces of Masvingo (9), Midlands (9), and Matabeleland South (2). See report and map at, http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/temp/reports/en_fup_0000016243_20150227_155204.pdf

See also commentaries in ProMED-mail post 20140520.2484074. - Mod.CRD]
